<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NakamaStream - En Desarrollo</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Bienvenido a NakamaStream actualmente la plataforma no se encuentra terminada">
    <meta property="og:title" content="NakamaStream">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Bienvenido a NakamaStream actualmente la plataforma no se encuentra terminada">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/168317328?s=200&v=4">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://nakamastream.lat/">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="NakamaStream">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Bienvenido a NakamaStream actualmente la plataforma no se encuentra terminada">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/168317328?s=200&v=4">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'custom-red': '#ff6b6b',
                        'custom-orange': '#ff8c00',
                        'custom-purple': '#6a0dad',
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'bounce-slow': 'bounce 3s infinite',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-white min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-6">
                <img src="https://github.com/NakamaStream/Resources/raw/main/NakamStream-logo-HD-removebg.png?raw=true" alt="NakamaStream Logo" class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto animate-bounce-slow" />
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-custom-red mb-4">NakamaStream</h1>
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">¡Estamos trabajando en algo increíble!</h2>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-8">La plataforma de NakamaStream aún no está terminada, pero pronto podrás disfrutar de tu contenido favorito.</p>
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4 mb-8">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 loading-box bg-gray-200 rounded-lg animate-pulse"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 loading-box bg-gray-200 rounded-lg animate-pulse"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 loading-box bg-gray-200 rounded-lg animate-pulse"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto progress-container bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-2">Progreso estimado:</p>
                <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-4">
                    <div class="bg-custom-red h-4 rounded-full" style="width: 100%"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Nueva sección para el enlace de Discord -->
            <div class="mt-8">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-2">Para más información, únete a nuestro Discord:</p>
                <a href="https://discord.gg/nakamastream" class="flex items-center justify-center text-custom-purple hover:text-custom-red">
                    <i class="fab fa-discord fa-2x mr-2"></i> 
                    Unirse al Discord
                </a>
            </div>
            <!-- Botón para ver el historial de releases -->
            <div class="mt-4">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-2">Ver el historial de releases:</p>
                <a href="/releases" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2 bg-custom-orange text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-custom-red transition duration-300">
                    Ver Releases
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-100 text-center p-4 mt-8 flex justify-between items-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600">&copy; 2024 NakamaStream. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
